<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AWGP Seva Portal - Contact</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/a96a0fdf1a.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        .navbar {
            background-color: rgb(35, 1, 255);
        }
        .navbar-brand, .nav-link {
            color: white !important;
        }
        .feedback-container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .feedback-form input, .feedback-form textarea {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .feedback-form button {
            width: 100%;
        }
        .feedback-image img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">AWGP Seva Portal</a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/api/v1/user-dashboard">Home</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/api/v1/about">About</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/api/v1/contact">Contact</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#">Help</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#"><i class="fas fa-user-circle"></i></a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container feedback-container">
        <h3 class="text-center">Share Your Feedback Here</h3>
        <p class="text-center">Feel free to share your feedback here. Your feedback matters for us</p>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-6 feedback-form">
                <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Name">
                <input type="email" class="form-control" placeholder="Email">
                <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Subject">
                <textarea class="form-control" rows="4" placeholder="Message"></textarea>
                <button class="btn btn-success">Submit</button>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 feedback-image d-none d-lg-block">
                <img src="/images/skj.jpg" alt="Feedback Image">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <p class="text-center mt-4">ॐ भूर्भुवः स्वः तत्सवितुर्वरेण्यम् भर्गो देवस्य धीमहि धियो यो नः प्रचोदयात्॥</p>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
